---
title: Harissa and Honey-Glazed Chicken Breasts with Almond Couscous and Garlic Sauce
description: Smoky, fragrant and gently spicy harissa meet sweet and sticky honey to create bold, caramelized flavor in this succulent chicken dish.  A creamy garlic-lemon sauce brings balance and dimension to both the chicken and couscous.
